{"title":"Best Tire Levers of 2021 – Pry Off Even the Tightest Bike Tire with Ease","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/22/best-tire-levers-bicycle/","date":1626956689000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Tire levers are such a basic item that they’re rarely given much thought…until, like us, you’ve used a lot of them and start to appreciate the nuances in design and function that make some way, way better than others.</p><p>For seasoned riders, they might be an afterthought, just get whatever’s on sale and throw in in your saddlebag or pack. For newbies, they may seem like an “extra” that only serious riders need… until you find yourself on the side of the road or trail trying desperately to pry a flat tire off of a rim with your bare hands.</p><p>Tire levers allow you to quickly—and cleanly—remove your tire from your rim with significantly less effort. They save your fingers, your tire rim, and possibly, the rest of your ride. And after testing a lot of them, here are our picks for the very best tire levers for every type of cyclist…</p><p><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/clever-standard-tire-lever-with-bicycle-chain-quick-link-remover-tool-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/clever-standard-tire-lever-with-bicycle-chain-quick-link-remover-tool-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/clever-standard-tire-lever-with-bicycle-chain-quick-link-remover-tool-1.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/clever-standard-tire-lever-with-bicycle-chain-quick-link-remover-tool-1-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/clever-standard-tire-lever-with-bicycle-chain-quick-link-remover-tool-1-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/clever-standard-tire-lever-with-bicycle-chain-quick-link-remover-tool-1-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.co