.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-297x91.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-800x246.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-120x37.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-768x236.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-1536x472.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-696x214.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-1068x328.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155610/unior-tire-levers-1366x420.jpg 1366w\"></a></p><p>Specifically designed to be comfortable in your hand, the Unior tire levers are great for tricky, tight tires. Some levers can be hard to hang onto, but the ergonomically-friendly silhouette makes these levers easy to grasp when you need to push hard to move a tough tire.</p><p>Bonus points for having a nearly foolproof spoke catcher -this design works much better than a looped hook- keeping one lever firmly in place while you slide the other around. Plus, they click together, making them easy to find in your pack.</p><ul><li>Color: <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00IWRX01E/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blue</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00QHD63HS/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Black</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00QHD63HS/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Green</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00QHD63HS/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Red</a></li><li>Dimensions: 122mm length, 34 grams</li><li>Price: $10</li></ul><h3><span>&nbsp;<strong>BEST BUDGET TIRE LEVERS:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=e295c418-295a-447c-b265-734e25f82503&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F705651%2Fpedros-tire-levers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pedro’s Tire Levers</a>&nbsp;</span></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516508212.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554.jpg\" alt=\"pedros tire levers\" width=\"1212\" height=\"536\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554.jpg 1212w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554-297x131.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554-800x354.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554-120x53.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554-768x340.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554-696x308.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/05155603/pedros-tire-levers-e1625516608554-1068x472.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/20